data.description:
Come check out this 3 bedroom and 1 full bath ranch on a quiet neighborhood street. This home features hardwood floors throughout, wood burning fireplace in living room and a decent sized kitchen with SS appliance. Outside you will find a large yard with a patio. Septic tank was replaced in June of 2023.
SELLERS ARE REQUESTING BEST AND FINAL ON 1/15 at 9PM.
